code: import http from"../http-common";class ArtWalkPublishedDataService{getAll(){return http.get("/artwalks/published");}get(id){return http.get("/artwalks/published/".concat(id));}create(data){return http.post("/artwalks/published",data);}update(id,data){return http.put("/artwalks/published/".concat(id),data);}delete(id){return http.delete("/artwalks/published/".concat(id));}deleteAll(){return http.delete("/artwalks/published");}findByTitle(title){return http.get("/artwalks/published?title=".concat(title));}}export default new ArtWalkPublishedDataService();
